# CLAUDE Is Canonical

- Treat `CLAUDE.md` at the repository root as canonical for work in this repo.
- Follow its Fumapress/Waku architecture, content conventions, and command set.
- Engine API truth lives in the sibling `blit386` repo (`docs/`); the public pages here are GENERATED from it by
  `scripts/sync-docs-from-engine.mjs` (`pnpm run sync:docs`). Never hand-edit generated pages under `content/docs/**` or
  `src/data/api-history.generated.json`. See `CLAUDE.md` (Documentation mirror).
- Use repo commands exactly as documented in `CLAUDE.md` (`pnpm run preflight`, not bare `pnpm preflight`).
